{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e0162b7576","title":"对志愿军火炮筹补方案的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aeaef5c62f","index":0,"year":1952,"month":5,"day":14,"articleId":"e0162b7576"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"3474c38b09","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会副主席、中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀1952年5月14日报告上写给周恩来的批语。"},{"id":"09ecbe7f92","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指彭德怀转呈的中国人民解放军炮兵司令员陈锡联，副司令员万毅、苏进，副政治委员邱创成1952年5月13日关于志愿军火炮损失情况及筹补方案。方案提出：（一）从新改装步兵师中抽调新进口的炮兵装备全部补充志愿军。（二）志愿军按每师装备1个炮兵团，需补充野炮、榴弹炮共计1250门。如向苏方订货需外汇56235830卢布。"},{"id":"6578058b5c","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭，指彭德怀。爱，指衰荣臻，当时任中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会代理总参谋长。票，指票裕，当时任中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会副总参谋长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0c50c7696c","type":"title","text":"对志愿军火炮筹补方案的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576"},{"id":"3474c38b09","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576"},{"id":"09ecbe7f92","type":"paragraph","text":"此事以解决办法，除你所说的几个炮团调去以外，请考虑（一）从国内守备各军调一部分，（二）从在朝二线各军调一部分。是否可能，请与彭、悬、乘商讨决定为盼！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576"},{"id":"6578058b5c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576"},{"id":"143f8467e6","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576"},{"id":"87b96b819f","type":"paragraph","text":"此外，向友方购炮，是否可能，请再研的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576"}],"page":{"id":"3f13feb658","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e0162b7576","start":109,"end":109}}}},"__N_SSG":true}